      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Support devices consisting of pieces of wood, metal, stone, or other material that project from or overhang a wall, arch, a beam, or shelf to carry weight, or for purely ornamental purposes. Brackets are sometimes worked into volutes, scrolls, or other motifs.</Note_Text>
